- USD currency formatting without NGN conversion
- Non-accessible color combinations
- Components without loading states
- Forms without proper validation
- Desktop-only interactions (hover-dependent UX)
- Heavy animations that impact 3G performance
- American date formats (MM/DD/YYYY)
```

